{"tid":121211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲群起鬧法官咒「絕子絕孫」 隨時犯藐視法庭罪？","createTime":"2017-02-15T05:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T11:21:48.000Z","uid":77196,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0821613e775132aeadcf0858dd9a47e681a54c2","tid":121211,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170215/56306877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170215%2F56306877&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=4e712b5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170215%2F56306877&h=3b56e767\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170215/56306877</a><br />\n<br />\n七警暗角打人在事發兩年後，昨終有裁決，法官裁定各被告蓄意導致身體受嚴重受傷罪名不成立，而較輕的襲擊致造成身體傷害罪成。雖然七警被判以較輕罪名，但一眾藍絲卻對裁決表示極度不滿，紛紛在網上辱罵今次判決的法官，甚至作出人身恐嚇。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲facebook專頁「9up新聞」更貼出案件法官杜大衛的相片，不滿七警需要還押，更寫上「去死啦你！」又指杜是「狗官」。<br />\n<br />\n該帖引來大批激進藍絲留言，主要留言針對法官杜大衛，指本身為外國人的杜是「港英餘孽」，甚至咀咒他全家「死絕」、「絕子絕孫」。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲又發起遊行，周六3時半從中環遮打花園出發，途經警察總部後到政府總部，反對法官決定。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，在網上恐嚇及辱罵法官，隨時會犯上「藐視法庭罪」。在2015年7月，裁判官陳碧橋就「光復元朗」反水貨客示威案判刑，自宣判女示威者以胸襲警罪成後，不斷受到威嚇，當時網上出現要陳碧橋「小心睇路」，更有攻擊其家人的言論，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警方重案組其後接手調查，相信有人在網上平台發佈內容含有恐嚇成份留言，拘捕一涉案男子</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得一視同仁呀警犬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96076a615b21ce4425e79fde30ef80ebfc0a4b42","tid":121211,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04408abbbb96daf603d9bf3b48c3f04935865e31","tid":121211,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:10:10.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔啱佢哋心水就咩都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39b6e82ff5e7b3999edf64ecb93e5e3a81e0066","tid":121211,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n<br />\n警察亂鳩咁黎,官公平做野就咒個官<br />\n<br />\n市民亂鳩咁黎,官公平做野就大叫抵死<br />\n<br />\n班撚樣識唔識分咩叫對咩叫錯? 盲撐就=對?<br />\n<br />\n仲要覺得自己係岩果下真係好撚野"},{"pid":"4d71e004606a119c0d02b81d60582dafbe1eb532","tid":121211,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:12:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63a192bc62bdee49b9fe8ed258ef0cf0511097c1","tid":121211,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑死<br />\n<br />\n警察亂鳩咁黎,官公平做野就咒個官<br />\n<br />\n市民亂鳩咁黎,官公平做野就大叫抵死<br />\n<br />\n班撚樣識唔識分咩叫對咩叫錯? 盲撐就=對?<br />\n<br />\n仲要覺得自己係岩果下真係好撚野</blockquote><br />\n班友盲撐政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6b66e94cd0c28006bc414f23b3a06dfc647ee1","tid":121211,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"支持法官出傳令告班藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6862f7964459296bf51dd246a9b3df11db14a0","tid":121211,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:19:17.000Z","msg":"屋企嗰件廢老都屌緊法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb25f6b0028c14c8b20a15f24f9a5c3f7ed797db","tid":121211,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e330e4136ac8cd061aaf7a0857112b467a6b496","tid":121211,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"之前屌李唯治嗰啲高登仔都一次過告埋啦"},{"pid":"3190ad768611f31e0ddf57db35198054a467d9da","tid"