blockquote><br />\n咁你屌果個係咪法官呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e2e01a28e39ef052f23e9129755bb2f1809460","tid":121211,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>即係以言入罪！？<br />\n以後隨口講句：「你去扑街死啦。」<br />\n分分鐘都拉得wor。。。</blockquote><br />\n你係咪覺得自己講野好有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係拉＋告得入<br />\n而後係條街講句「XXX，你去死啦」<br />\n都可以拉！<br />\n<br />\n後果係好嚴重！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你知唔知乜撚野叫藐視法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係你果個偉大既蝗國無呢條罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}